        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。\n且住，看这花郎，面目清秀，十分英俊，因何落魄至此啊？\n丫鬟，将这花郎带进花园，我要周济与他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦！那一花郎随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喔，参见小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，这一花郎，你家住哪里？姓甚名谁？因何落到这般光景？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卑人薛平贵，乃长安人氏。晓读诗书，略通武艺。只因父母早亡，闻得苏元帅\n招兵将，为此，沿途乞讨，前去投军报国，怎奈天气寒冷，腹中饥饿，困倒在\n此，啊！真正困煞人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "落魄之身当发奋，\n有心立志去投军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言来自思忖，\n他家贫却是有志的人。\n我有意与他订下亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又恐丫鬟一旁听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "抛球选婿事不稳、彩楼之事对他论、王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这一花郎你可曾用过饭么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……惭愧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，看这花郎饿得甚是可怜，速去取些银米过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一花郎，你方才言道父母双亡，但不知家中可有……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有妻室否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐说哪里话来，落在乞讨之中，哪有银钱娶妻室呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴有一言，不好启齿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐有话请当面。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我实对你说了吧，我父亲为我终身大事，定于二月二日，在十字街前，高搭彩\n楼，抛球招婿。不知你前来接彩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多承小姐如此见爱，感恩非浅，怎奈落魄之人，怎配相府千金，还望小姐三思！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我既以身相许，你……你……又何必迟疑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那抛球招婿，必是王孙公子，哪有花郎之分？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无妨，到了那日你早些站在楼前，我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "理当遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二月二日事有准，\n请君听我说分明：\n万事只怕有心的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，银米在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "付于花郎，叫他去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎，你把银米拿去，谢过小姐，你快走吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢小姐，平贵告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别小姐出园门，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤那花郎转来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎回来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐有话快言明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩楼之事你须守信，\n莫做薄情无义人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐不必细叮咛，\n平贵岂是无义人？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回房去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心中暗把秦晋订，\n愿与薛郎结良姻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏、丫鬟同下。）"
        }
      ],
